Introduction

The Deep is an independent singer-songwriter under the label talented. She was previously part of the co-ed duo Morethan7. Her solo debut took place on March 8, 2019, with the digital single "Don't Wanna Be." In December 2019, she collaborated with Basick on his song titled "CHOCO."
